short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Delete only your logs, not everyone elses!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Tired of accidently deleting debug logs of other users?

Install this extension and see / delete only your logs, right from the debug logs screen, with just one click!

Now with an option of "Delete All Logs" or show / delete a particular user's logs.
